INSTALL

1) Install rvm (http://beginrescueend.com/)
   * use whichever method appropriate for your OS
2) Install bundler (http://gembundler.com/)
   $ sudo gem install bundler
3) $ sudo rvm install 1.8.7
4) $ bundle exec gem update --system 1.5.3
5) $ bundle install
6) $ bundle exec script/server

NOTES:

- If bundle install has problems insalling the MySQL gem, try:

  $ bundle config build.mysql --with-mysql-config=/path/to/mysql_config
     * example: bundle config build.mysql --with-mysql-config=/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysql_config
